Package it.polimi.ingsw.client.MessageFromServer.Updates

  • Class Summary
    Class Description
    UpdateActiveLeaderCard
    Message from the server: it notifies that a specified leader card has been activated by specific player.
    UpdateDevCardDrawn
    Message from the server containing color and level of the development card that has just been bought.
    UpdateDevDeck
    Message from server: it contains the ID of the development card just bought by the specified player and the position in which has been placed.
    UpdateDiscardLeaderCard
    Message from server: it contains the ID of the leader card that has just been discarded by a specified player.
    UpdateDrawToken
    Message from server: it contains the ID of the action token which has just been drawn.
    UpdateExtraSlot
    Message from server: it contains type and quantity of resources placed by a specified player in a specific leader card (ID).
    UpdateFaithpath
    Message from server: contains all the faithpath's positions after the last update.
    UpdateLastProduced
    Message from server: it contains all the resources produced by a specified player.
    UpdateMarketColumn
    Message from server: it contains all the marbles inside the column that has just been changed and the new outer marble.
    UpdateMarketRow
    Message from server: it contains all the marbles inside the row that has just been changed and the new outer marble.
    UpdateMeetingPope
    Message from server: it is sent when someone reaches a meeting pope position.
    UpdateStrategyBuffer
    Message from server: it contains the IDs of the leader cards selected as strategies for the market.
    UpdateStrongbox
    Message from server: contains all the resources owned by a specified player in his strongbox.
    UpdateWarehouseDepot
    Message from server: it contains the shelf of a specified player that has been changed.
